<h2>Your Rights</h2>
<p>You may request deletion of your account and data at any time by contacting us at <a href="mailto:bugbuddy35@gmail.com">bugbuddy35@gmail.com</a>.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, feel free to contact us at the email above.</p>
